
config BR2_PACKAGE_ENCFS
	bool "encfs"
	depends on BR2_PACKAGE_BOOST
	depends on BR2_PACKAGE_RLOG
	depends on BR2_PACKAGE_LIBFUSE

	help
	EncFS provides an encrypted filesystem in user-space. It runs without any special permissions and uses the FUSE library module to provide the filesystem interface. EncFS is open source software, licensed under the GPL (with the underlying library released under the LGPL).

	https://vgough.github.io/encfs/
	http://www.arg0.net/encfs	
	http://encfs.googlecode.com/files/encfs-1.7.4.tgz
